features: Weather protection: The wind-resistant fabric features a durable water repellent(DWR)finish that effortlessly sheds light rain
Breathability: Engineered from breathable fabrics with extra panels of lasered holes under the arms and back to increase airflow, the jacket helps you manage your body temperature

Super lightweight & compact: This minimalist jacket makes lightness a priority with supple waist and wrist elastics for a closer fit and no added weight. It packs down tiny with the pocket in the lining
AdvancedSkin Shield: AdvancedSkin technical fabrics improve body comfort by keeping you dry, warm and protected when you need it and where you need it
DWR treatment: Durable water repellent, or DWR, is a coating added to fabrics at the factory to make them water-resistant(or hydrophobic)
Laser cut ventilation: Little holes in the fabric improve air flow and ventilation of your garment
